dc_title_s: Iberian Peninsula 1:250,000: Setubal, sheet 57. Series A.M.S. M581
dc_description_s: United States. Army Map Service. North Decimal Degree 39.0000. South Decimal Degree 38.0000. East Decimal Degree -8.0000. West Decimal Degree -9.0000. Alternate title: Setubal, Portugal. Polyconic projection. With Portuguese-English glossary. Relief shown by 100 m. contour interval, gradient tint and spot heights. Standard map series designation: A.M.S. M581. "Compiled from Portugal, 1:50,000, Servicos Geodesicos, 1904-38; Portugal, 1:50,000, Instituto Geografico, sheet 38, 1930 and 39, 1936; Portugal, 1:250,000, Estador Maior do Exercito, 1936-37; Road Map of Spain and Portugal, 1:1,400,000, G.S.G.S., 1942, corrected from Intelligence Reports, 1942-1943. Partially revised from aerial photography, 1942.".
